      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 63,
      "message": "Why name of data store is inconsistent ?\n----------------------------------------\n1. Why we are not using \"org.onap.cps.ncmp.api.impl.operations.DatastoreType#PASSTHROUGH_RUNNING\" or\norg.onap.cps.ncmp.api.impl.operations.DatastoreType#PASSTHROUGH_OPERATIONAL ?\n\n2. Why \"passthrough-running\" or \"passthrough-operational\" is hardcoded where into enum org.onap.cps.ncmp.api.impl.operations.DatastoreType has data store name \"ncmp-datastore:passthrough-running\" and \"ncmp-datastore:passthrough-operational\"?",
